<item>
            <title>[LU-17520] change logic of setting DEBUG_SIZE in test-framework</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17520</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Now by default the size of DEBUG_SIZE is 2MB multiplied by number of cpu. This way lustre debug buffer could be just 4MB on a system with 2 CPUs, despite 3GB RAM. It is the reason why often time period in debug logs doesn&apos;t scope the reason of failure(sometimes depending on log level debug buffer stores just several seconds).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
